# SharpMod

An open source implementation of Mono into Valve's Source Engine, allowing developers to extend the game writing C# and other .NET langauges. 

### Current features

1. Client and server side coding.
2. Custom entities - Support input/output events, networked variables, inheritance, and animations.
3. Simple particle system - Draw lots of light weight triangles on your screen.
4. Panels - Create custom panels to draw on the client. 
5. Physics - Enable custom physics on entities. 
